column5: I have a johnson seahorse 10 hp. Need to know year and mod.#.The tag from the trans. bracket is missing.The welch plug ser# is 1865160. Looking at some pictures a 1959 looks very similar except my fuel tank has two lines (1 fuel / 1pressure) Please help!
Nice motor. Welcome aboard....didn't the good folks at IBoats answer all your questions?
yes thank you,I got what I needed from iboat.thanks again
I'm guessing a 56. i had one just like it in an 18hp. I tossed it in the garbage after it let me down one to many times. I used to pull my guts out on that motor
